### spectator

spectator

Player / spectator mode selection

Values:

- 0: Player
- 1: Spectator; Normal 3rd person view
- 2: Spectator; 1st person view (see _sp_cl_spectator_distance). Only on SoFplus servers.
- 3: Spectator; Same as `1`, but you will see player health / armor / weapon info if that has been enabled on the server. Only on SoFplus servers.
- 4: spectator; Same as `2`, but you will see player health / armor / weapon info if that has been enabled on the server. Only on SoFplus servers.
